=Once, twice, three times a Gold Logie |work=[[The Sydney Morning Herald]] |url=https://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/once-twice-three-times-a-gold-logie-20050502-gdl8io.html |department=News and Features | page=3|date=2 May 2005}}</ref>\n\n===Gold Logie===\n{| class=wikitable width=\"50%\"\n|-\n! width=\"25%\"| [[Gold Logie Award for Most Popular Personality on Australian Television|Most Popular Personality on Australian Television]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''[[Rove McManus]] in ''[[Rove (TV series)|Rove (Live)]]'' ([[Network Ten]])'''\n**[[Bridie Carter]] in ''[[McLeod's Daughters]]'' ([[Nine Network]])\n**[[Bec Cartwright]] in ''[[Home and Away]]'' ([[Seven Network]])\n**[[Georgie Parker]] in ''[[All Saints (TV series)|All Saints]]'' (Seven Network)\n**[[John Wood (Australian actor)|John Wood]] in ''[[Blue Heelers]]'' (Seven Network)\n|}\n\n===Acting/Presenting===\n{| class=wikitable width=\"100%\"\n|-\n! width=\"25%\"| [[Logie Award for Most Popular Actor|Most Popular Actor]]\n! width=\"25%\"| [[Logie Award for Most Popular Actress|Most Popular Actress]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''[[John Wood (Australian actor)|John Wood]] in ''[[Blue Heelers]]'' ([[Seven Network]])\n**[[Beau Brady]] in ''[[Home and Away]]'' (Seven Network)\n**[[Chris Hemsworth]] in ''Home and Away'' (Seven Network)\n**[[Aaron Jeffery]] in ''[[McLeod's Daughters]]'' ([[Nine Network]])\n**[[Glenn Robbins]] in ''[[Kath & Kim (Australian TV series)|Kath & Kim]]'' ([[ABC1|ABC TV]])\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''[[Bec Cartwright]] in ''[[Home and Away]]'' ([[Seven Network]])'''\n**[[Jane Allsop]] in ''[[Blue Heelers]]'' (Seven Network)\n**[[Bridie Carter]] in ''[[McLeod's Daughters]]'' ([[Nine Network]])\n**[[Gina Riley]] in ''[[Kath & Kim (Australian TV series)|Kath & Kim]]'' ([[ABC1|ABC TV]])\n**[[Magda Szubanski]] in ''Kath & Kim'' (ABC TV)\n|-\n! width=\"50%\"| [[Logie Award for Most Outstanding Actor in a Series|Most Outstanding Actor in a Series]]\n! width=\"50%\"| [[Logie Award for Most Outstan