stralian TV series)|The Great Outdoors]]'' ([[Seven Network]])\n**''[[Renovation Rescue]]'' (Nine Network)\n|-\n! width=\"50%\"| [[Logie Award for Most Popular Reality Program|Most Popular Reality Program]]\n! width=\"50%\"| Most Popular Overseas Program\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''''[[Australian Idol]]'' ([[Network Ten]])'''\n**''[[Big Brother (Australian TV series)|Big Brother 4]]'' (Network Ten)\n**''[[The Block (Australian TV series)|The Block]]'' ([[Nine Network]])\n**''[[My Restaurant Rules]]'' ([[Seven Network]])\n**''[[RPA (TV series)|RPA]]'' (Nine Network)\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''''[[The O.C.]]'' ([[Network Ten]])'''\n**''[[The Bill]]'' ([[ABC1|ABC TV]])\n**''[[CSI: Crime Scene Investigation]]'' ([[Nine Network]])\n**''[[ER (TV series)|ER]]'' (Nine Network)\n**''[[Friends]]'' (Nine Network)\n|-\n|}\n\n===Most Outstanding Programs===\n{| class=wikitable width=\"100%\"\n|-\n! width=\"50%\"| [[Logie Award for Most Outstanding Drama Series|Most Outstanding Drama Series]]\n! width=\"50%\"| Most Outstanding Mini Series or Telemovie\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''''[[Love My Way]]'' ([[Fox8]])'''\n**''Love Bytes'' (Fox8)\n**''[[Fireflies (TV series)|Fireflies]]'' ([[ABC1|ABC TV]])\n**''[[Stingers (TV series)|Stingers]]'' ([[Nine Network]])\n**''[[The Secret Life of Us]]'' ([[Network Ten]])\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''''[[Jessica (TV miniseries)|Jessica]]'' ([[Network Ten]])'''\n**''[[The Alice]]'' ([[Nine Network]])\n**''The Brush Off, Murray Whelan Series'' ([[Seven Network]])\n**''[[Small Claims]]'' (Network Ten)\n**''Through My Eyes: The Lindy Chamberlain Story'' (Seven Network)\n|-\n! width=\"50%\"| Most Outstanding Comedy Program\n! width=\"50%\"| Most Outstanding Sports Coverage\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''''[[The Chaser Decides]]'' ([[ABC1|ABC TV]])'''\n**''Derrick'', Episode 2 ([[The Comedy Channel]])\n**''[[John Safran vs God]]'' ([[SBS1|SBS TV]])\n**''[[Kath & Kim (Australian TV series)|Kath & Kim]]'' ([[ABC1|ABC TV]])\n**''Bobo and Pauly: The Early Years'