w Female Talent]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''[[Chris Hemsworth]] in ''[[Home and Away]]'' ([[Seven Network]])'''\n**[[Ben Nicholas]] in ''[[Neighbours]]'' ([[Network Ten]])\n**[[Dean O'Gorman]] in ''[[McLeod's Daughters]]'' ([[Nine Network]])\n**[[Jason Smith (actor)|Jason Smith]] in ''Home and Away'' (Seven Network)\n**[[Wil Traval]] in ''[[All Saints (TV series)|All Saints]]'' (Seven Network)\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''[[Natalie Blair]] in ''[[Neighbours]]'' ([[Network Ten]])'''\n**[[Indiana Evans]] in ''[[Home and Away]]'' ([[Seven Network]])\n**[[Rachel Gordon]] in ''[[Blue Heelers]]'' (Seven Network)\n**[[Natalie Saleeba]] in ''[[All Saints (TV series)|All Saints]]'' (Seven Network)\n**[[Samantha Tolj]] in ''Blue Heelers'' (Seven Network)\n|-\n! width=\"50%\"| [[Logie Award for Most Popular Presenter|Most Popular TV Presenter]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''[[Rove McManus]] in ''[[Rove (TV series)|Rove (Live)]]'' ([[Network Ten]])'''\n**[[Andrew Denton]] in ''[[Enough Rope|Enough Rope with Andrew Denton]]'' ([[ABC1|ABC TV]])\n**[[Jamie Durie]] in ''[[Backyard Blitz]]'' ([[Nine Network]])\n**[[David Koch (analyst)|David Koch]] in ''[[Sunrise (Australian TV program)|Sunrise]]'' ([[Seven Network]])\n**[[Andrew O'Keefe]] in ''[[Deal or No Deal (Australian game show)|Deal or No Deal]]'' (Seven Network)\n|}\n\n===Most Popular Programs===\n{| class=wikitable width=\"100%\"\n|-\n! width=\"50%\"| [[Logie Award for Most Popular Drama Program|Most Popular Australian Drama Series]]\n! width=\"50%\"| [[Logie Award for Most Popular Light Entertainment Program|Most Popular Light Entertainment or Comedy Program]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''''[[McLeod's Daughters]]'' ([[Nine Network]])'''\n**''[[All Saints (TV series)|All Saints]]'' ([[Seven Network]])\n**''[[Blue Heelers]]'' (Seven Network)\n**''[[Home and Away]]'' (Seven Network)\n**''[[Neighbours]]'' ([[Network Ten]])\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''''[[Rove (TV series)|Rove (Live)]]'' ([[Network Ten]])'''\n**''[[Dancing with the 